title: Wholesale Price of Aluminum for New York
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1913-1934 (2)--Original Data, 1933-1941. This Segment Refers To Only 99% Pure Aluminum. Source: 1933-1934 Data Direct From Bls. Remainder From Bls Bulletins And "Wholesale Prices."

This NBER data series m04179b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 4 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter04.html.
